description:
"

Women's Nike running shoes, Air Zoom Vomero 11: luxurious comfort and incredible speed.
Most comfortable version ever made up to now, the Nike Air Zoom Vomero + 11-Woman is made of softer materials than its predecessor and offers a magical combination of cushioning and reactive speed.

SOFT
Lunarlon cushioning kilometers. The foam is firmer on the back of the foot and softer midfoot for smooth transitions from heel to toe.

RESPONSIVE CUSHIONING
The Nike Zoom Air unit in the heel and forefoot offer responsive cushioning and lightweight ideal for travels faster. The soft material placed on top of the unit in the heel provides superior comfort and a silky smooth ride.

OPTIMIZED FIT
The redesigned Flymesh offers optimal fit/> forefoot while providing breathability and support. The new softer materials into the collar offer ideal comfort while the foam tongue ensures maximum cushioning on top of foot to reduce pressure on the laces.

MORE INFORMATION
Full inner sleeve length for a perfect fit.
Flywire midfoot wrap the cables for a supportive fit and adaptable.
Rubber outsole side crash rail to absorb impacts.
Segmented rubber for flexibility.
Rubber with pressure point mapping for a neutral and efficient gait.

Color: Avio/Cyclamen/White/Black.

"@en

description:
"
                                    A newly designed tri-star outsole pattern adjusts to your foot's every step, delivering support and flexibility.The new Nike Free Run Flyknit draws upon new studies that reveal how the foot expands and contracts upon impact with the ground. For this reason, Nike designers have developed an auxetic midsole that allows it to splay upon impact without it thinning out (think about stretching an elastic band, which thins out when it’s pulled apart and is then compromised at its weakest point). Spreading across two planes, the geometric tri-star form mimics how the body and foot react to force and accounts for the massive changes in foot size (approximately one size in length and two sizes in width) that occur throughout a runner’s stride to deliver support and flexibility.Revolutionary, never before used Soft Foam provides comfort and cushioning without compromising natural motion.Flywire technology is integrated with the laces and Flyknit upper for a dynamic midfoot fit, along with asymmetrical lacing that follows the natural lines of the foot to help reduce lace pressure.Please be advised that the Nike Free shoe collection seems to be coming up slightly large by half a size and as a result we recommend considering half a size smaller.Features Include:Strong lightweight Flyknit upper construction provides a sock-like fit.Low-profile cushioning and rounded heel encourage natural footstrike.Auxetic tri-star outsole pattern expands with your step for flexible cushioning.Flywire cables integrate with the laces for a dynamic midfoot fit.Notch in the collar allows for easy on and off.Asymmetrical lacing follows the natural lines of the foot to help reduce lace pressure.
                                "@en

Leichte Gummi-Segmente unter den Zehen und Ferse für Traktion und Strapazierfähigkeit.

description:
"
                                    The Nike Free 3.0 V4 is a new shoe from Nike with key new features that gives the runner supreme flexibility for the most natural-feeling barefoot-like ride.Numerous deep flex grooves promote Nike's most natural stride, while the seamless upper provides lightweight support and the mesh inner sleeve offers a sock -like fit.New and better really does apply to the Free 3.0 V4, utilising Nanoply throughout the upper, which is a micro-layer of engineered composite material that is laser-perforated for a skin-like fit that moves with each stride. The larger perforations are strategically placed in areas that need more flexibility while the smaller perforations are in areas that demand more support. The arch has been modified with transtarsal diagonal flex cuts for enhanced twisting, strengthening, and natural motion flexibilityIn the Nike Free continuum, the lower the number in a shoe’s name, the closer it comes to barefoot running (on the continuum, 10.0 represents conventional footwear while zero represents the bare foot). The Nike Free 3.0 shoe is the closest Nike has come to delivering a truly barefoot experience for optimal foot strengthening and flexibility.Ball-to-Heel offset = 4mm differential heel to forefoot drop: The lower the number, the closer to to ground you are and the more it stretches your Achilles tendon. This helps you run more naturally and barefoot-like.The Nike Free 3.0 v4 is ideal if you’re a runner who wants the strengthening benefits of barefoot training, but you don’t want to sacrifice the underfoot protection or multi-surface traction of footwear.
                                "@en
title: "Nike Free Trainer 3.0 V4 - Black/Green/Solar/White"@en " Mens Shoes Nike Black/Green/Solar/White 749361-034 "@en

description:
"
                                    Inizia ogni attacco sul campo con le nuove scarpe da calcio Nike Tiempo 6. Indossate da Gerard Piqué, Jérôme Boateng e Andrea Pirlo, la sesta generazione delle Tiempo Legend porta avanti la sua reputazione di non avere rivali per la vestibilià, il tocco e la trazione per stabilire una nuova era per questo classico moderno.Lavorando in congiunzione con la struttura a gabbia del mesopiede, il controtallone modellato si  conformarsi alla forma naturale del piede per evitare qualsiasi slittamento del tallone, mentre un tessuto in microfibra sopra la soletta aiuta anche a eliminare qualsiasi movimento del piede all'interno della scarpa.Per offrire una vestibilità degna del titolo Tiempo Legend, queste scarpe sono dotate di una nuova costruzione con linguetta integrata per evitare qualsiasi slittamento.Per un maggiore supporto e bloccaggio del piede, le Tiempo Leggend 6 includono una struttura interna in microfibra sul mesopiede per portare la tomaia più vicina al piede e ottimizzare il tocco sulla palla.Lavorando in congiunzione con la struttura a gabbia del mesopiede, il controtallone modellato si  conformarsi alla forma naturale del piede per evitare qualsiasi slittamento del tallone, mentre un tessuto in microfibra sopra la soletta aiuta anche a eliminare qualsiasi movimento del piede all'interno della scarpa.TOCCO:Per un controllo immediato sulla palla, le Tiempo Legend VI dispongono di una tomaia in pelle di canguro adaptive sull'avampiede. La pelle è compressa sottovuoto all'interno della struttura a gabbia per dare un effetto trapuntato, per un tocco superiore quando si passa e si riceve la palla.La pelle compressa sottovuto riduce la quantità di assorbimento dell'acqua permettendo all tomaia  di rimanere morbida e leggera, mentre la tecnologia ACC (All Conditions Control) offre un controllo della palla sia in condizioni di asciutto che di bagnato.Sei tacchetti intercambiabili di 11mm sull'avampiede e di 13 mm sul tallone permettono la massima trazione su campi da compatti a morbidi, mentre cinque tacchetti fissi TPU assicurano un migliore controllo. Le Tiempo Legend VI rappresentano un nuovo livello di prestazione per scarpe da calcio su campi naturali morbidi. Per evitare gli accumuli di fango che producono un peso eccessivo, il piatto suola di queste scarpe include la tecnologia proprietary che assicura anche un'ottima trazione in tutte le condizioni di tempo.
                                "@it

description:
"
                                    Il detto: "Se non è rotto, non aggiustarlo" non si applica qui. Nonostante le Hypervenom fossero ottime scarpe sotto qualsiasi punto di vista, Nike ha adottato la filosofia del continuo miglioramento – la Perfezione si Evolve.Ingannevoli di natura, le scarpe da calcio Nike HyperVenom Phantom II FG sono studiate per un'agilità senza pari su terreni naturali compatti. La loro tomaia NIKESKIN testurizzata rende più facile il controllo della palla e migliora il tocco.I cavi Flywire in combinazione con il collare Dynamic Fit avvolgono il piede per creare un ottimo supporto e stabilità. Hanno una costruzione che segue una forma sagomata anatomicamente corretta per offrire una maggiore velocità e una calzata perfetta per la massima agilità.La tecnologia (ACC) offre un controllo della palla affidabile sia in condizioni di bagnato che di asciutto, mentre i tacchetti hanno le punte in TPU una trazione che sia adatta alle condizioni del campo.Un sistema di allacciatura più corto massimizza l'area di battuta di queste HyperVenom Phantom mentre i lacci sono più sottili nella parte più bassa per una superficie più uniforme. All'interno della scarpa, una soletta preformata ammortizza il piede e aiuta a ridurre la pressione dei tacchetti, per un maggiore comfort e minori distrazioni.Un telaio in nylon con una base Pebax® offre un buon supporto pur mantenendo una sensibilità reattiva, mentre il design della piastra con alluce diviso serve per migliorare ulteriormente l'agilità.HYPERVENOM II - NON PUOI FERMARE CIÒ CHE NON PUOI VEDERE.

description:
"
                                    GIOCA VELOCE. PENSA VELOCELa nuova generazione delle scarpe da calcio Nike Magista II porta la creatività a un nuovo livello. Progettata per centrocampisti intelligenti come Mario Götze, Blaise Matudi e Javier Pastore che creano opportunità di attacco per la loro squadra.VESTIBILITÀLe Magista Obra 2 dispongono di una nuova tomaia Flyknit, che è stata progettata per eliminare ogni spazio intorno al piede per una calzata a pennello.Lavorati a maglia direttamente nella tomaia sulla parte mediale e laterale, i cavi Flywire delle Magista alimentano un sistema di blocco del piede che impedisce di scivolare all'interno della scarpa, mentre un tallone interno mantiene la caviglia stabile e sicuro.Riprogettato per collegare la parte inferiore della gamba e il piede, il collare Dynamic Fit è modellato per adattarsi al profilo naturale del malleolo per una vestibilità più sicura e protettiva, mentre la sua costruzione a maglia stretta assicura un migliore mantenimento della forma.TOCCOUn nuova Flyknit termoformata crea una tomaia 3-D testurizzata per un maggiore attrito sulla palla, mentre la tecnologia ACC (All Conditions Controlled) fornisce un tocco costante sulla palla sia sul bagnato che sull'asciutto.I lacci sono stati leggermente spostati per creare una superficie di battuta più ampia, mentre la costruzione tongue-less ha come caratteristica un'imbottitura che assicura un tocco reattivo sulla palla.TRAZIONEPiù leggera rispetto alla versione precedente, la piastra delle Magista vede una riduzione di Pebax dal suo suo telaio in nylon, riducendo il suo peso complessivo da 85g a 62g. Questa riduzione permette al piede di avvicinarsi a terra, il che significa una migliore sensibilià e reattività nei cambi di direzione.La configurazione dei tacchetti delle Magista è stata creata utilizzando Fine Element Analysis (FEA), che è un metodo computerizzato che produce dati per progettare una piastra ideale per la trazione rotazionale su campi naturali compatti.
                                "@it
title: "Nike Magista Obra II FG - Rio Teal/Volt/Ossidiana/Giada Clear"@it " Nike Scarpe Uomo Firm Ground Teal/Volt/Obsidian/Clear Jade "@it

description:
"
                                    Elevating the original Air Max 90, these kicks show off perforated synthetic leather uppers for incredibly lightweight, breathable comfort and not to mention style. Nike Air Max Origins Nike's revolutionary Air-Sole unit made its way into Nike footwear in the late '70s. In 1987, the Nike Air Max 1 debuted with visible air in its heel, allowing fans more than just the feel of Air-Sole comfort — suddenly they could see it. description:
"

Wearing you the running shoes from Nike Free 5.0 for flexibility as barefoot.
The running shoe Nike Free 5.0-woman combines a highly flexible sole and low profile for absolutely natural movements to cushioning, grip and support of a traditional running shoe.

ORIGINS OF THE NIKE FREE SHOE
After discovering that Stanford athletes are trained barefoot on the golf course of their universities, three of the most creative and innovative Nike began to develop a shoe that can provide the light and natural feeling of barefoot running. In 2002 examined a group of men and women by binding their feet of the insoles can measure pressure values and using high-speed cameras to take pictures of moving feet.
The team has spent eight years studying the Biomechanics of running without shoes. The results have made it possible to achieve a deep understanding of the angle of the foot's natural impact, pressure and position of the fingers, allowing designers to create a Nike running shoe flexible and unconventional both inside and out.

Everyday flexibility
The new hexagonal Flex grooves are carved in hot soles and wrap the side wall allowing the foot to move more naturally in every direction.

Support and ventilation
The mesh upper lace knitting is reinforced with forefoot Flywire for lightweight ventilation, a custom fit and a support that follows your movements.

Natural gait
The heel follows the shape of the foot and the movement on the ground to facilitate a more natural step.

8 mm differential
With a difference of 8 mm between the height of the heel and the forefoot, the Nike Free 5.0 delivers the highest differential of the full range of running shoes Nike Free for superior cushioning the benefits associated with the reinforcement of the foot through natural movements.

Other advantages
Outer layers without seams for maximum support and resistance without appesantirti
The traditional tongue to absorb the pressure of laces
The minimal insole fits the curvature of the foot for superior comfort and support
Waffle structure in the sole to absorb impacts and increase responsiveness

Weight: 186 g (size 37.5 woman)
Color: Black/White.

"@en

description:
"
                                    The third in a series of seven cleats chronicling Cristiano Ronaldo’s journey, Chapter 3 focuses on the game that brought him to the attention of one of the world’s biggest clubs. To celebrate the moment of his discovery, the Nike Mercurial Superfly features a dark green that’s inspired by his original club colours and neon accents to represent his shining talent.  FITDeveloped around the idea of a racecar fit, the Superfly V features a new V16 last, which is designed to engage the major metatarsal by shaping the outsole to the natural contours of your foot. This allows the metatarsals to sit lower in the boot while the big toe is slightly raised, increasing flex across the joint and allowing you to generate maximum power when sprinting off the mark.Constructed with a Flyknit and NikeSkin upper, the Superfly features an upgraded tongue less construction, while the Flywire cables within the upper are independently able to react to how the foot is engaging with the ground for optimal lockdown. To reduce the loss of elasticity over time, the Dynamic Fit collar has a tighter knit construction to enhance your proprioception with the ground, while its internal anti-skid top cloth eliminates any foot movement within the boot.TOUCHTo enhance your touch and feel, the Superfly V features a new 3-D textured Speed Rib construction, which is knitted into the cleat’s Flyknit upper to create increased friction on the ball for high-speed control.  Applied with Nike’s All Conditions Control (ACC) Technology, the Superfly provides consistent levels of grip on the ball in wet and dry weather conditions.TRACTIONRedesigned to improve your acceleration, the Superfly’s chassis is made from compressed Nylon, which is 40% lighter than the Carbon Fibre plate used for the Superfly IV. description:
"
                                    Elaborée par Nike à partir d'une empeigne révolutionnaire en cuir de kangourou souple et avec un filet hydrophobe, la chaussure de football Legend V SG-Pro est extrêmement légère et le restera.Le cuir de kangourou doux sur l'avant-pied procure un toucher de balle naturel inégalé qui constitue la marque de fabrique des chaussures de football Tiempo depuis près de vingt ans, le Kanga-Lite réduit le poids et les nouvelles technologies développées par Nike remettent la chaussure au goût du jour.La technologie HyperShield bloquant l'humidité permet à la Legend V d'absorber 73% moins d'eau que sa prédécesseure et de sécher beaucoup plus vite, tandis que la technologie ACC garantit une adhérence fiable dans toutes les conditions météorologiques.Conçue à partir d'un modèle anatomique avec un contrefort interne, la Legend V procure une tenue confortable et ajustée au pied grâce à une semelle intérieure perforée et prémoulée avec des inserts Poron pour un confort ultime.La plaque en TPU sur toute la longueur s'allie à la semelle interne pour permettre à ces chaussures de football Nike une transition en douceur du pied intermédiaire jusqu'à l'avant-pied et une flexibilité multi-directionnelle.La configuration des crampons SG-Pro présente des crampons fixes et deux ensembles de crampons vissés en aluminium (11/13 mm et 13/15 mm) pour une adhérence polyvalente, un plus grand confort et une maîtrise du pied sur les terrains gras.

description:
"

Running shoes from Asics man, model GT-2000 3.
Never again ran concluded in advance because of the wrong shoes, thanks to slight GT-2000 3. A perfect shoe to point to their objectives in the marathon and also excellent for post-race recovery.
The foot can count on maximum stability, regardless of distance travelled. The shape of the heel keeps your foot in place, preventing irritation and blistering.
Evolution of the legendary GEL-2130

Applied technology:
-Impact Guidance System: the basic design philosophy ASICS ® that uses linked components to optimize the natural movement of the foot from the heel to the support detachment.
ComforDry ™ Sockliner-: removable inner lining that provides cushioning performance and anti-microbial properties for a cooler, dry and healthy.
-FluidRide: the latest evolution in technology for ASICS midsoles. FluidRide provides the greatest benefits in terms of responsiveness and cushioning while remaining lightweight.
SpEVA ® Midsole Material-: improves the elasticity and reduces wear of the midsole.
-Discrete Eyelets |:: eyes positioned independently disperse the tension of the strings, creating a custom fit and optimising the comfort of the upper.
-Removable Sockliner: buttonholes placed independently disperse the tension of the strings, creating a custom fit and optimising the comfort of the upper.
-AHAR +: new blown AHAR outsole material. Provides to the foot greater absorption, durability and ride.
-Guidance: Trusstic system, Trusstic integrates implementation Guidance to maximize gait efficiency and ensuring the structural integrity in the middle part of the foot.
-Clutch Counter: a fitting structure that provides increased support and creates an optimum fit to the heel.
-55 Lasting SpEVA: ASICS midsoles material sets a new standard in the insole technology thanks to the optimization of cushioning and comfort.
-Light AHAR sponge: a blown AHAR outsole rubber from highly abrasion resistant material for greater strength, coupled with a cushioned, comfortable fit.
California Slip Lasting: for a better stability and comfort. The upper is stitched around a canvas or EVA Board before being attached to the midsole.
-Dynamic Duomax: the next generation DuoMax system provides added comfort and enhances gait efficiency.
Rearfoot and Forefoot-GEL ® Cushioning System: attenuates shock during support and detach and allows movement in multiple planes as the foot step in the cycle.
-3 m Reflective: reflective material produced by the company 3 m, for greater safety at night.
Solyte ® Midsole Material-: a lighter than standard midsole than the EVA and SpEVA ® by ASICS. It also features a better cushioning and durability.
-Guidance Line: flexible vertical Groove decouples the machine along the line of progression, to optimize the efficiency of gait.

Color: Blue/lime green/black/white.

"@en
title: "ASICS GEL GT 2000 3"@en apparel and sports equipment"@en 3 - MAN RUNNING SHOES Asics colour Blue T500N 4207 Athletic footwear

description:
"
                                    Il detto: "Se non è rotto, non aggiustarlo" non si applica qui. Nonostante le Hypervenom fossero ottime scarpe sotto qualsiasi punto di vista, Nike ha adottato la filosofia del continuo miglioramento – la Perfezione si Evolve.Ingannevoli di natura, le scarpe da calcio Nike HyperVenom Phantom II da uomo SG-Pro sono studiate per un'agilità senza pari su terreni naturali morbidi. La loro tomaia NIKESKIN testurizzata rende più facile il controllo della palla e migliora il tocco.I cavi Flywire in combinazione con il collare Dynamic Fit avvolgono il piede per creare un ottimo supporto e stabilità. Hanno una costruzione che segue una forma sagomata anatomicamente corretta per offrire una maggiore velocità e una calzata perfetta per la massima agilità.La tecnologia (ACC) offre un controllo della palla affidabile sia in condizioni di bagnato che di asciutto, mentre i tacchetti in alluminio intercambiabili sono disponibili in 2 lunghezze per una trazione che sia adatta alle condizioni del campo.Un sistema di allacciatura più corto massimizza l'area di battuta di queste HyperVenom Phantom mentre i lacci sono più sottili nella parte più bassa per una superficie più uniforme. description:
"
                                    The new Nike Free RUN draws upon new studies that reveal how the foot expands and contracts upon impact with the ground. For this reason, Nike designers have developed an auxetic midsole that allows it to splay upon impact without it thinning out (think about stretching an elastic band, which thins out when it’s pulled apart and is then compromised at its weakest point). Spreading across two planes, the geometric tri-star form mimics how the body and foot react to force and accounts for the massive changes in foot size (approximately one size in length and two sizes in width) that occur throughout a runner’s stride to deliver support and flexibility.Revolutionary, never before used Soft Foam provides comfort and cushioning without compromising natural motion.Offering breathability with an engineered mesh upper, the new Free RUN incorporates Flywire technology integrated with the laces for an adaptive, supportive fit.Features Include:Engineered mesh upper supports as it moves with you.Low-profile cushioning and rounded heel encourage natural footstrike.Auxetic tri-star outsole pattern expands with your step for flexible cushioning.Flywire technology integrated with the laces for an adaptive supportive fit.Offset: 8mm Last: QD-39
                                "@en

description:
"Nike Air Max BW
Dunkelblau/Weiss-Schwarz
881981-400
Genau so stellt sich jeder einen ansehnlichen Sportschuh vor, der nicht nur in seinem Stil einiges zu bieten hat, sondern auch mit seiner Technik glänzt. Der Nike Air Max BW Midnight Navy wird bei dieser Ausführung stolz in Dunkelblau, Weiß und Schwarz zur Schau gestellt. Sneakerfreunde werden sich über diese Farbgebung freuen und können Luftsprünge dank eingebauter Luftpolsterung ohne spätere Folgeschäden durchführen.
Was sich im Obermaterial wiederfinden lässt, stellt sich als Meshstoff heraus und überzieht außer der Zehentasche sowie Teile der Seiten den Oberschuh in Dunkelblau. Eine dunkelblaue Trennlinie aus synthetischem Stoff umrandet den ganzen Schuh einmal. Darüber wurde ein Schweif aus Gummi wiederholt in Dunkelblau gelegt, der einen eindrucksvollen Ausdruck präsentiert. An dem Hacken sieht man Air Max als Namen aus Gummi in Dunkelblau. Noch weiter in Richtung Sohle behauptet sich eine Perforierung wieder in Dunkelblau.
Die Füße können in weichen Meshstoff in Dunkelblau tauchen und fühlen sich, im Inneren angekommen, gleich pudelwohl. Angedeutet wird der Name "Nike Air" auf der Zunge erneut in Dunkelblau. Seitlich sind Schnürsenkelösen in Plastik eingearbeitet worden, die Halt für die dunkelblauen Bänder liefern. Kleine Plastikapplikationen in Dunkelblau setzen sich neben diese Halterung und peppen den oberen Teil des Schuhes Ton in Ton auf.
In die Zwischensohle baut Nike die viel gelobte Luftkammern-Technik (Air-Technologie) ein, die beim Auftritt für eine Dämpfung sorgt. Sie ist zusammen mit einem Teil der Sohle in Weiß ein absoluter Hingucker und zieht die Blicke förmlich auf sich. Durch kleine Fenster aus Kunststoff kann in das Technik-Zentrum gesehen werden und man bekommt ein Gefühl für die schon seit vielen Jahren bekannte Einbauweise. Als Laufsohle wurde schwarzes Gummi verwendet, das auch zur Wasserabweisung dient und einen festen Stand gewährt.
Fazit:
Unserer Meinung nach lassen sich diese Sneakers sowohl in der Freizeit als auch für diverse Sportarten tragen. Gerade wer Stabilität als wichtiges Attribut ansieht, hat mit dem Nike Air Max BW die richtige Wahl getroffen. Super bequem und außerdem zu vielen Kleidungsstücken kombinierbar ist der Schuh der perfekte Begleiter im Alltag.
Eigenschaften:

Leder und Synthetik sichern eine Langlebigkeit des Sneakers ab
Farbwahl von Dunkelblau, Weiß und Schwarz
Extra großes Sichtfenster verleiht Blick auf die Air-Dämpfungseinheit
Laufsohle aus Gummi in Schwarz

"@de

description:
"
                                    The new Nike Free RUN draws upon new studies that reveal how the foot expands and contracts upon impact with the ground. For this reason, Nike designers have developed an auxetic midsole that allows it to splay upon impact without it thinning out (think about stretching an elastic band, which thins out when it’s pulled apart and is then compromised at its weakest point). Spreading across two planes, the geometric tri-star form mimics how the body and foot react to force and accounts for the massive changes in foot size (approximately one size in length and two sizes in width) that occur throughout a runner’s stride to deliver support and flexibility.Revolutionary, never before used Soft Foam provides comfort and cushioning without compromising natural motion.Offering breathability with an engineered mesh upper, the new Free RUN incorporates Flywire technology integrated with the laces for an adaptive, supportive fit.Features Include:Engineered mesh upper supports as it moves with you.Low-profile cushioning and rounded heel encourage natural footstrike.Auxetic tri-star outsole pattern expands with your step for flexible cushioning.Flywire technology integrated with the laces for an adaptive supportive fit.Offset: 8mm Last: QD-39
                                "@en
title: "Nike Free Run - White/Black"@en " Nike Mens Shoes White/Black "@en

description:
"
                                    THE SCIENCE OF SPEEDThe next generation Nike Mercurial Vapor is akin to a formula one car, utilising scientific innovations to ensure Eden Hazard, Willian and Franck Ribéry are the fastest players on the pitch.FITDeveloped around the idea of a racecar fit, the Vapor features a new V16 last, which is designed to engage the major metatarsal by shaping the outsole to the natural contours of your foot. This allows the metatarsals to sit lower in the boot while the big toe is slightly raised, increasing flex across the joint and allowing you to generate maximum power when sprinting off the mark.Constructed with a Teijin synthetic upper, the Vapor features a tongue less construction to wrap the foot for a snug fit, while the internal anti-skid sock liner eliminates any movement within the boot.TOUCHTo enhance your touch and feel, the Vapor features a new 3-D textured Speed Rib construction to ensure high-speed control. Applied with Nike’s All Conditions Control (ACC) Technology, the Vapor’s upper provides consistent levels of grip on the ball in wet and dry weather conditions.TRACTIONMore responsive and shaped to the anatomical V-16 last, the compressed nylon soleplate features chevron shaped studs for quick ground penetration, release and braking on firm natural grass surfaces.
                                "@en
title: "Nike Mercurial Vapor XI FG - Black/Pink Blast"@en " Nike Mens Boots Firm Ground Blast "@en

description:
"
                                    LA SCIENZA DELLA VELOCITA 'La nuova generazione di scarpe da calcio Nike Vapor XI è simile a una vettura di Formula Uno e utilizza innovazioni scientifiche per garantire a giocatori come Cristiano Ronaldo, Alexis Sanchez e Antonio Marziale di andare il più veloce possibile.VESTIBILITÀSviluppate intorno all'idea di una prestazione da macchina da corsa, le Vapor sono caratterizzate da una nuova forma V16, che è stata progettata per coinvolgere il metatarso, modellando la suola al naturale profilo del piede. Questo permette al metatarso di posizionarsi più in basso all'interno della scarpa, mentre l'alluce rimane leggermente sollevato in modo da  aumentare la flessibilità e generare la massima potenza negli scatti.Realizzate con una tomaia sintetica Teijin, le Vapor dispongono di una rinnovata costruzione priva di linguetta, mentre il sottopiede anti-skid elimina qualsiasi movimento all'interno della scarpa.TOCCOPer migliorare il tocco e la sensibilià, le Vapor dispongono di un nuova costruzione testurizzata  3-D Speed Rub per un migliore controllo ad alta velocità e sono dotate di tecnologia (ACC) per una presa sulla palla affidabile in qualsiasi condizione di tempo.TRAZIONEMaggiormente reattiva e realizzata con forma anatomical V-16, la piastra in nylon compresso dispone di tacchetti a forma chevron per una penetrazione, un rilascio e una frenata più rapidi su campi naturali compatti.

All'interno di queste scarpe da calcio, una gabbia 'agility' usa una fascia di supporto alla zona mediale e laterale di queste scarpe HyperVenom Phantom per una migliore stabilità. Un sistema di allacciatura più corto massimizza l'area di battuta di queste HyperVenom Phantom mentre i lacci sono più sottili nella parte più bassa per una superficie più uniforme. L'imprevedibilità richiede agilità ed è per questo che Nike ha utilizzato un telaio in nylon leggero e reattivo con una base Pebax che è divisa al centro dell'avampiede, dalla punta verso l'interno. Rispecchiando la forma del piede, le scarpe da calcio HyperVenom Phantom sono state costruite su una forma anatomicamente corretta per una calzata a pennello e incorporano una soletta ammortizzante che minimizza la pressione dei tacchetti. description:
"



FREE TO GO FURTHER
The Nike Free RN Distance Women's Running Shoe features Lunarlon cushioning with large hexagonal flex grooves for more natural motion with the soft comfort you need for longer runs.
Move Naturally 
The natural-motion outsole features hexagonal flex grooves that offer six points of flexibility, allowing your feet to move the way they were meant to.
Soft Cushioning 
The lightweight Lunarlon cushioning system delivers miles of soft responsiveness. It fuses soft foam and a lightweight Phylon carrier to deliver an excellent blend of plush comfort and durable support to go the distance.
Breathable Comfort 
Single-layer, engineered knit helps keep your feet cool, while Flywire cables integrated with the laces wrap your arch for an adaptive, supportive fit.
More Details 

Partial inner sleeve wraps your forefoot in breathable comfort
Deconstructed mesh heel provides support and breathability
Solid rubber segments under the toe for enhanced traction and durability
Anatomical heel enables more natural motion
Weight: 207 grams (women's size 5.5)

Nike Free Origins 
After learning that Stanford athletes had been training barefoot on the university's golf course, three of Nike's most innovative and creative employees set out to develop a shoe that felt natural and weightless, similar to bare feet. The team spent eight years studying the biomechanics of runners' feet in motion. The results yielded a profound understanding of the foot's natural landing angle, pressure and toe position, allowing Nike designers to build an unconventional and flexible running shoe from the inside out.

description:
"
                                    The Nike Free 3.0 V4 is a new shoe from Nike with key new features that gives the runner supreme flexibility for the most natural-feeling barefoot-like ride.Numerous deep flex grooves promote Nike's most natural stride, while the seamless upper provides lightweight support and the mesh inner sleeve offers a sock -like fit.New and better really does apply to the Free 3.0 V4, utilising Nanoply throughout the upper, which is a micro-layer of engineered composite material that is laser-perforated for a skin-like fit that moves with each stride. The larger perforations are strategically placed in areas that need more flexibility while the smaller perforations are in areas that demand more support. The arch has been modified with transtarsal diagonal flex cuts for enhanced twisting, strengthening, and natural motion flexibilityIn the Nike Free continuum, the lower the number in a shoe’s name, the closer it comes to barefoot running (on the continuum, 10.0 represents conventional footwear while zero represents the bare foot). The Nike Free 3.0 shoe is the closest Nike has come to delivering a truly barefoot experience for optimal foot strengthening and flexibility.Ball-to-Heel offset = 4mm differential heel to forefoot drop: The lower the number, the closer to to ground you are and the more it stretches your Achilles tendon. This helps you run more naturally and barefoot-like.The Nike Free 3.0 v4 is ideal if you’re a runner who wants the strengthening benefits of barefoot training, but you don’t want to sacrifice the underfoot protection or multi-surface traction of footwear.
                                "@en
title: "Nike Free Trainer 3.0 V4 - Black/Team Red/University Red/Volt"@en " Mens Shoes Nike Red/Volt 749361-066 "@en

description:
"

Running shoes/women's Asics Gel Cumulus 17 race: the great innovation meets the best features ever!
The award-winning series of GEL-Cumulus continues to improve, with the 17th version that boasts a top of the range FluidRide ™ midsole and GEL Cushioning unit in the heel and forefoot even bigger without gaining weight. In addition, Cumulus 17 is the most comfortable ever thanks to seamless construction. Neutral to slightly astonished by runners wearing the lighter version and pronators remain more cushioned GEL-Cumulus series ever created.

Applied technology:
-FluidRide technology in the midsole provides the ultimate combination of rebound and damping properties with low weight and durability. The top layer of the midsole is gum mixed, made to maximize comfort. The layerbottom of the midsole is made from a lighter, flexible rubber mixture, allowing the shoe to provide greater responsiveness.
-Rearfoot and Forefoot GEL: The ASICS GEL System is based on a special kind of silicone that acts as a great cushion for shocks. Gel units are strategically in the midsole to create specific positions and functions.
-Guidance Trusstic System ™: the Trusstic System integrates the building Guidance Line for an improved efficiency while providing the structural integrity the forefoot.
-Guidance Line ™: vertical Flex Groove for greater efficiency in stride.
-ASICS High Abrasion Resistance rubber is placed in areas of greatest impact of the outsole to reduce excessive wear. AHAR + is thinner and lighter than the AHAR
-Channels located underneath the midfoot andd the heel to increase flexibility and cushioning.
-I.G.S. (Impact Guidance System): in order to meet the demand of various specialities of Athletics the I.G.S. (Impact Guidance System) is a design philosophy designed to follow the natural movement of the athlete's foot.
-Speva sockliner: provides optimal cushioning, creating a cooler, drier and healthier environment for the foot.
-Lace Eyelets placed independently to give proper tension, creating a customized environment and greater comfort.
-Seamless Construction: seamless materials reduces the risk of abrasions and irritations.

Color: Purple/Blue/White.

description:
"
                                    The Nike Free 3.0 V4 is a new shoe from Nike with key new features that gives the runner supreme flexibility for the most natural-feeling barefoot-like ride.Numerous deep flex grooves promote Nike's most natural stride, while the seamless upper provides lightweight support and the mesh inner sleeve offers a sock -like fit.New and better really does apply to the Free 3.0 V4, utilising Nanoply throughout the upper, which is a micro-layer of engineered composite material that is laser-perforated for a skin-like fit that moves with each stride. The larger perforations are strategically placed in areas that need more flexibility while the smaller perforations are in areas that demand more support. The arch has been modified with transtarsal diagonal flex cuts for enhanced twisting, strengthening, and natural motion flexibilityIn the Nike Free continuum, the lower the number in a shoe’s name, the closer it comes to barefoot running (on the continuum, 10.0 represents conventional footwear while zero represents the bare foot). The Nike Free 3.0 shoe is the closest Nike has come to delivering a truly barefoot experience for optimal foot strengthening and flexibility.Ball-to-Heel offset = 4mm differential heel to forefoot drop: The lower the number, the closer to to ground you are and the more it stretches your Achilles tendon. This helps you run more naturally and barefoot-like.The Nike Free 3.0 V4 is ideal if you’re a runner who wants the strengthening benefits of barefoot training, but you don’t want to sacrifice the underfoot protection or multi-surface traction of footwear.
                                "@en

                                    Conçues pour les joueurs techniques qui prennent le contrôle du jeu, les chaussures de football Concave Halo+ Microfibre FG ont une empeigne en microfibre synthétique texturée souple, tandis que les inserts externes en caoutchouc moulé sur l'empeigne permettent plus d'accroche et donc de contrôle du ballon.Le Concave Component sur la partie supérieure des lacets améliore les frappes en créant une plus grande zone de contrôle permettant un contact parfait avec le ballon.Les Halo+ intègrent la technologie F3 (Football Form Fit), un système de double laçage unique offrant un soutien et une tenue comme sur mesure à toutes les formes de pied sans déformer leur forme naturelle.A l'intérieur, la doublure innovante Fusion Lining s'associe à l'empeigne pour lui permettre de conserver sa forme, tandis que la semelle de propreté légère moulée en EVA amortit contre les chocs et est ultra confortable.Pour plus de contrôle et de stabilité sur les terrains secs, la semelle extérieure est en TPU et les crampons à lamelles et ovales permettent une adhérence optimale.

description:
"
                                    The 6th iteration Tiempo Legend furthers its reputation for providing unrivalled fit, touch and traction to establish a new era for this modern classic.FIT:To provide a fit worthy of the Tiempo Legend title, the boots features a new integrated tongue construction, which will ensure the tongue won’t slide providing a consistent fit. For support and increased lock down, the Tiempo Legend 6 includes an internal microfibre cage in the midfoot to bring the upper closer to the foot, providing a 1-to-1 fit.Working in tandem with the midfoot cage, the moulded heel counter will conform to the natural shape of the foot to prevent any heel slippage, while a microfibre cloth on top of the insole also works to eliminate any foot movement within the boot.TOUCH:For instant control on the ball, the Tiempo Legend 6 features adaptive K-leather on the vamp of the boots. This leather is vacuum pressed to the interior cage to provide a quilted effect, for superior touch when kicking for touch.With the leather vacuum pressed, this reduces the amount of water uptake to keep the upper remaining soft and light, while ACC (All Conditions Control) technology provides optimal control when kicking in both wet and dry conditions.TRACTION:A full length engineered TPU plate and insole board work together to provide these Nike boots with a smooth transition from midfoot to forefoot and multi-directional flexibility.The SG-Pro stud configuration features fixed studs and two sets of screw-in aluminium studs (11/13mm and 13/15mm) for versatile traction, comfort and underfoot control on soft ground.
                                "@en

description:
"


You'll never again have to cut short your run because of your shoe, thanks to the lightweight GT-2000 3. It's the go-to shoe for taking aim at your marathon targets, and it's there for you all the way to the post-race recovery zone.
It's built to keep your foot stable, whether you're doing a half-marathon or the whole thing. It cuts the risk of chafing and blisters, and it makes every stride a stable one with a heel counter that clamps your foot in place.

Impact Guidance System (I.G.S) - ASICS design philosophy that employs linked componentry to enhance the foot's natural gait from heel strike to toe-off.
FluidRide - FluidRide provides the ultimate combination of bounce back and cushioning properties with reduced weight and exceptional durability.
Dynamic DuoMax Support System - This evolution of DuoMax system enhances stability and support, with reduced weight and increased platform support.
Rearfoot and Forefoot GEL Cushioning Systems - Attenuates shock during impact and toe-off phases, and allows movement in multiple planes as the foot transitions through the gait cycle.
Guidance Trusstic System - This Trusstic System integrates Guidance Line construction for enhanced gait efficiency while providing midfoot structural integrity.
Guidance Line - Vertical flex groove decouples the tooling along the line of progression for enhanced gait efficiency.
Heel Clutching System - Exoskeletal heel counter provides improved support and creates improved heel fitting environment.
Discrete Eyelets - Independently placed eyelets disburse lace tension, creating a customized fitting environment and enhanced upper comfort.
ComforDry™ Sockliner - Provides cushioning performance and anti-odor properties for a cooler, drier, healthier environment.

                                    THE SCIENCE OF SPEEDThe next generation Nike Mercurial Vapor is akin to a formula one car, utilising scientific innovations to ensure Eden Hazard, Willian and Franck Ribéry are the fastest players on the pitch.FITDeveloped around the idea of a racecar fit, the Vapor features a new V16 last, which is designed to engage the major metatarsal by shaping the outsole to the natural contours of your foot. This allows the metatarsals to sit lower in the boot while the big toe is slightly raised, increasing flex across the joint and allowing you to generate maximum power when sprinting off the mark.Constructed with a Teijin synthetic upper, the Vapor features a tongue less construction to wrap the foot for a snug fit, while the internal anti-skid sock liner eliminates any movement within the boot.TOUCHTo enhance your touch and feel, the Vapor features a new 3-D textured Speed Rib construction to ensure high-speed control. Applied with Nike’s All Conditions Control (ACC) Technology, the Vapor’s upper provides consistent levels of grip on the ball in wet and dry weather conditions.TRACTIONMore responsive and shaped to the anatomical V-16 last, the compressed nylon soleplate features chevron shaped studs for quick ground penetration, release and braking on firm natural grass surfaces.
                                "@en
title: "Nike Mercurial Vapor XI FG - Black/Pink Blast"@en " Nike Mens Soccer Cleats Firm Ground Blast "@en

description:
"
More cushioned than the Nike Free RN Motion Flyknit, the Nike Free RN Women's Running Shoe features a newly designed midsole pattern that expands, flexes and contracts with your foot with every step. Its lightweight, breathable mesh upper helps keep your feet cool and comfortable from start to finish.
MOVE NATURALLY
The next-generation Nike Free midsole expands in multiple directions thanks to an entirely new tri-star pattern, adding a new dimension of flexibility that lets your feet move more dynamically with every stride. Plus, the heel is rounded to mimic the shape of your foot and roll naturally with the ground.
SOFT CUSHIONING
Softer than previous iterations, the new midsole foam delivers exceptionally comfortable cushioning and lightweight durability for miles.
FLEXIBLE, BREATHABLE SUPPORT
Engineered mesh provides lightweight, flexible support and breathable comfort. Flywire cables integrate with the laces and can be adjusted for an adaptive fit.
MORE DETAILS

Minimal sockliner moulds to the shape of your foot for added support
Lightweight solid rubber segments under the toe and heel for enhanced traction and durability
Weight: 196 grams (women's size 5.5)

NIKE FREE ORIGINS
After learning that Stanford athletes had been training barefoot on the university's golf course, three of Nike's most innovative and creative employees set out to develop a shoe that felt natural and weightless, similar to bare feet. The team spent eight years studying the biomechanics of runners' feet in motion. The results yielded a profound understanding of the foot's natural landing angle, pressure and toe position, allowing Nike designers to build an unconventional and flexible running shoe from the inside out. "@en
title: "Nike Free RN Women's Running Shoes FA16 404"@en 404 · Nike Barefoot Trainers ah"@en

description:
"

Scarpe da running da uomo di Asics, modello GT-2000 3.
Mai più corse concluse in anticipo per colpa delle scarpe sbagliate, grazie alla leggera GT-2000 3. Una scarpa perfetta per puntare ai propri obiettivi nella maratona e ottima anche per il recupero post-gara.
Il piede può contare sulla massima stabilità, indipendentemente dalla distanza percorsa. La conformazione del tallone mantiene sempre in posizione il piede, evitando irritazioni e vesciche.
Evoluzione della leggendaria GEL-2130

Tecnologia applicata:
- Impact Guidance System: filosofia alla base del design ASICS® che impiega componenti collegate per ottimizzare il movimento naturale del piede dall'appoggio del tallone allo stacco.
- ComforDry™ Sockliner: rivestimento interno rimovibile che fornisce prestazioni di ammortizzazione e proprietà antimicrobiche per un ambiente più fresco, asciutto e sano.
- FluidRide: l'evoluzione più recente nella tecnologia per intersuole ASICS. FluidRide fornisce i massimi vantaggi in fatto di reattività e ammortizzazione pur restando leggero.
- SpEVA® Midsole Material: migliora le caratteristiche di elasticità e riduce l'usura dell'intersuola.
- Discrete Eyelets: gli occhielli posizionati in modo indipendente disperdono la tensione dei lacci, creando una calzabilità personalizzata e ottimizzando il comfort della tomaia.
- Removable Sockliner: gli occhielli posizionati in modo indipendente disperdono la tensione dei lacci, creando una calzabilità personalizzata e ottimizzando il comfort della tomaia.
- AHAR+: nuovo materiale soffiato della suola AHAR. Fornisce al piede un maggiore assorbimento, resistenza e corsa.
- Guidance Trusstic: il sistema Trusstic integra la realizzazione Guidance per ottimizzare l'efficienza dell'andatura e assicurare l'integrità strutturale nella parte centrale del piede.
- Clutch Counter: una struttura esoscheletrica che fornisce un maggiore sostegno e crea una calzabilità ottimale per il tallone.
- SpEVA 55 Lasting: il materiale per intersuole ASICS fissa un nuovo standard nella tecnologia per solette grazie all'ottimizzazione di ammortizzazione e comfort.
- Light AHAR sponge: una suola in gomma AHAR soffiata dal materiale altamente resistente alle abrasioni per una maggiore resistenza, abbinato a una calzata comoda e ammortizzata.
- California Slip Lasting: per una migliore stabilità e comfort. La tomaia viene cucita intorno a un tela o a una tavola EVA per poi essere fissata all'intersuola.
- Dynamic Duomax: il sistema DuoMax di nuova generazione fornisce un maggiore comfort e ottimizza l'efficienza dell'andatura.
- Rearfoot and Forefoot GEL® Cushioning System: attenua gli urti nelle fasi di appoggio e stacco e consente il movimento in più piani di pari passo con il passaggio del piede nel ciclo del passo.
- 3M Reflective: materiale riflettente prodotto dall'azienda 3M, per una maggiore sicurezza notturna.
- Solyte® Midsole Material: un composto più leggero dell'intersuola rispetto agli standard EVA e SpEVA® di ASICS. Presenta inoltre una migliore ammortizzazione e resistenza.
- Guidance Line: la scanalatura flessibile verticale disaccoppia la lavorazione lungo la linea di progressione, per ottimizzare l'efficienza dell'andatura.

Colore: Blu/Verde lime/Nero/Bianco.

Worn by Gerard Piqué, Jérôme Boateng and Andrea Pirlo, the 6th iteration Tiempo Legend furthers its reputation for providing unrivalled fit, touch and traction to establish a new era for this modern classic.FIT:To provide a fit worthy of the Tiempo Legend title, the boots feature a new integrated tongue construction, which will ensure the tongue won’t slide providing a consistent fit. description:
"

Zapatillas Asics hombre, modelo GT-2000 3.
Nunca funcionó concluyó anticipadamente debido a los zapatos equivocados, gracias a la leve GT-2000 3. Un zapato perfecto para señalar sus objetivos en la maratón y también excelente para la recuperación después de la carrera.
Los pies pueden contar con la máxima estabilidad, independientemente de la distancia recorrida. La forma del talón mantiene su pie en su lugar, prevenir la irritación y ampollas.
Evolución de la legendaria GEL-2130

Tecnología aplicada:
-Sistema de guía impacto: el diseño básico filosofía ASICS ® que utiliza componentes vinculados para optimizar el movimiento natural del pie desde el talón para el destacamento de apoyo.
™ ComforDry Sockliner-: forro que interior extraíble proporciona rendimiento de amortiguación y propiedades antimicrobianas para una hielera, seca y saludable.
-FluidRide: la última evolución en tecnología para ASICS midsoles. FluidRide ofrece los mayores beneficios en términos de capacidad de respuesta y amortiguación al mismo tiempo restante ligero.
Material ® SpEVA Midsole: mejora la elasticidad y reduce el desgaste de la suela.
-Ojales discretos |:: ojos posicionados independientemente dispersan la tensión de las cuerdas, creando un ajuste personalizado y optimizar la comodidad de la parte superior.
-Desmontable Sockliner: ojales colocados independientemente dispersan la tensión de las cuerdas, creando un ajuste personalizado y optimizar la comodidad de la parte superior.
-AHAR +: nuevo material de suela AHAR soplado. Proporciona a la mayor absorción de pie, durabilidad y paseo.
-Dirección: Trusstic sistema Trusstic integra implementación orientación para maximizar la eficiencia de marcha y asegurar la integridad estructural en la parte media del pie.
-Contador embrague: una estructura de montaje que proporciona mayor apoyo y crea un óptimo ajuste hasta el talón.
-55 SpEVA duración: ASICS midsoles material fija un nuevo estándar en la tecnología de plantilla gracias a la optimización de amortiguación y comodidad.
-Luz esponja AHAR: un caucho de suela AHAR soplado de material altamente resistente a la abrasión para mayor resistencia, junto con un ajuste cómodo, amortiguado.
California Slip duración: para una mejor estabilidad y comodidad. La parte superior se sutura alrededor de una lona o EVA Board antes de estar vinculado a la suela.
-Duomax dinámica: la nueva generación de sistemas DuoMax proporciona mayor comodidad y mejora la eficiencia de la marcha.
Retropié y antepié-GEL ® sistema de amortiguación: atenúa choque durante el soporte y separar y permite el movimiento en planos múltiples mientras el pie un paso en el ciclo.
-3 m reflectante: material reflexivo producido por la empresa 3 m, para una mayor seguridad en la noche.
Material ComforDry ® entresuela: un encendedor que estándar entresuela de EVA y SpEVA ® by ASICS. También cuenta con una mejor amortiguación y durabilidad.
-Línea Dirección: ranura vertical flexible desconecta la máquina a lo largo de la línea de progresión, para optimizar la eficiencia de la marcha.

Color: Azul/verde verde/negro/blanco.

description:

Procurant plus d'adhérence et un toucher amélioré dans les conditions humides et sèches, Puma GripTex est un motif en 3D transparent appliqué sur la tige.La cage externe EverFit a été stratégiquement placée par Puma dans le pied intermédiaire pour une flexibilité optimale, une excellente stabilité et une meilleure résistance.Le contre-talon externe procure à cette chaussure une tenue sûre, tandis que la technologie Puma evoAptoLast épouse les contours naturels du pied pour une tenue parfaite.La semelle extérieure anatomiquement conçue présente la technologie Pebax Speedtrack pour des changements de direction et une réactivité améliorés.L'association de la technologie Duoflex et de petits crampons coniques moulés optimise la pénétration et la manoeuvrabilité sur les terrains secs.

Elle ne peut être utilisée que sur l'herbe naturelle et dans de bonnes conditions météorologiques. Mais les moments d'exception qu'elle t'offrira seront inoubliables.La tige en textile ultra-fin procure des sensations pied nu sur la balle, tout en réduisant le poids de la chaussure pour une extrême légèreté.La tige intègre la technologie Puma SPEEDFRAME qui soutient le pied dans les zones clés lors des accélérations sous fortes pressions. description:
"
                                    GRAJ SZYBKO. MYŚL SZYBCIEJ.Oferując natychmiastowe połączenie butów z mózgiem, następna generacja Nike Magista 2 zabiera kreatywność na nowy poziom. Przeznaczone dla inteligentnych rozgrywających takich jak Mario Götze, Blaise Matudi i Javier Pastore, którzy widzą możliwość ataku, kiedy inni nie widzą i biorą wszystkie szanse dla swojego zespołu.DOPASOWANIEDla idealnego dopasowania i czucia, Magista 2 Obra posiada Flyknit na powierzchni górnej zapewniając dopasowanie jak w skarpetce i eliminuje jakąkolwiek przestrzeń wokół stóp.Kable Flywire dziane bezpośrednio do części górnej i bocznej w butach Magista, biegną od oczka do strategicznej lini zgryzu, podczas gdy wewnętrzny zapiętek utrzymuje kostkę stabilną i bezpieczną.Przeprojektowany aby połączyć łydkę i stopę, Dynamiczny Kołnierz jest ukształtowany tak, aby dopasować się do naturalnego konturu Twojej kostki dla większej ochrony, podczas gdy ciaśniejsza konstrukcja zapewnia lepsze zachowanie kształtu.DOTYKNowa termiczna powierzchnia górna Flyknit, tworzy 3-D teksturę aby uzyskać więcej tarcia na piłkę, podczas gdy technologia ACC (Kontrola Wszystkich Warunków) zapewnia dobry kontakt z piłką zarówno w mokrych i suchych warunkach pogodowych.Sznurowadła zostały przesunięte lekko do przyśrodkowej strony, aby utworzyć większą powierzchnię podczas uderzania piłki, podczas gdy konstrukcja bez języka oferuje dodatkową amortyzację, aby zapewnić Ci idealny kontakt z piłką.TRAKCJALżejsze od poprzedniej wersji, podeszwa Magista ze zredukowanym Pebax dla nylonowej ramy, która zmniejsza ogólną wagę podeszwy z 85g do 62g. Redukcja ta pozwala bliżej zbliżyć się do ziemi, co oznacza lepszy i czulszy dotyk przy zmianie kierunku.Wzór kołków wykorzystywany do Magista został stworzony przy użyciu drobnoziarnistych elementów (FEA), które są skomputeryzowane tak, aby zapewnić idealną trakcję obrotową na twardych nawierzchniach gruntowych.UWAGA : Rozmiarówka butów Nike Kids Magista Obra II FG jest zaniżona. Cette chaussure a été conçue selon un modèle contouré anatomiquement correct et favorisant la vitesse offrant une tenue sur mesure pour un maximum d'agilité.La technologie All Conditions Control (ACC) assure un contrôle de la balle fiable dans toutes les conditions climatiques et les crampons en aluminium amovibles sont disponibles en 2 longueurs afin de permettre une adhérence personnalisée et te permettre de dominer le terrain, quelle que soit sa condition.La zone de laçage plus petite permet une plus grande zone de frappe pour un contact optimal avec le ballon et des frappes parfaites et précises.La semelle interne moulée amortit le pied afin de réduire les pressions des crampons et d'améliorer le confort et la concentration.La structure en Nylon avec une base Pebax® soutient le pied tout en maintenant des sensations réactives et la semelle se divisant au centre de l'avant-pied accroit l'agilité.
                                "@fr

description:
"
                                    Inizia ogni attacco sul campo con le nuove scarpe da calcio Nike Tiempo 6. Indossate da Gerard Piqué, Jérôme Boateng e Andrea Pirlo, la sesta generazione delle Tiempo Legend porta avanti la sua reputazione di non avere rivali per la vestibilià, il tocco e la trazione per stabilire una nuova era per questo classico moderno.Lavorando in congiunzione con la struttura a gabbia del mesopiede, il controtallone modellato si  conformarsi alla forma naturale del piede per evitare qualsiasi slittamento del tallone, mentre un tessuto in microfibra sopra la soletta aiuta anche a eliminare qualsiasi movimento del piede all'interno della scarpa.Per offrire una vestibilità degna del titolo Tiempo Legend, queste scarpe sono dotate di una nuova costruzione con linguetta integrata per evitare qualsiasi slittamento.Per un maggiore supporto e bloccaggio del piede, le Tiempo Leggend 6 includono una struttura interna in microfibra sul mesopiede per portare la tomaia più vicina al piede e ottimizzare il tocco sulla palla.Lavorando in congiunzione con la struttura a gabbia del mesopiede, il controtallone modellato si  conformarsi alla forma naturale del piede per evitare qualsiasi slittamento del tallone, mentre un tessuto in microfibra sopra la soletta aiuta anche a eliminare qualsiasi movimento del piede all'interno della scarpa.TOCCO:Per un controllo immediato sulla palla, le Tiempo Legend VI dispongono di una tomaia in pelle di canguro adaptive sull'avampiede. La pelle è compressa sottovuoto all'interno della struttura a gabbia per dare un effetto trapuntato, per un tocco superiore quando si passa e si riceve la palla.La pelle compressa sottovuto riduce la quantità di assorbimento dell'acqua permettendo all tomaia  di rimanere morbida e leggera, mentre la tecnologia ACC (All Conditions Control) offre un controllo della palla sia in condizioni di asciutto che di bagnato.Sei tacchetti intercambiabili di 11mm sull'avampiede e di 13 mm sul tallone permettono la massima trazione su campi da compatti a morbidi, mentre cinque tacchetti fissi TPU assicurano un migliore controllo. Le Tiempo Legend VI rappresentano un nuovo livello di prestazione per scarpe da calcio su campi naturali morbidi. Per evitare gli accumuli di fango che producono un peso eccessivo, il piatto suola di queste scarpe include la tecnologia proprietary che assicura anche un'ottima trazione in tutte le condizioni di tempo.
                                "@it
title: "Nike Tiempo Legend VI SG-Pro - Nero/Bianco/Nero/Oro Metallico"@it " Nike Scarpe Uomo Terreni Morbidi Metallico "@it

description:
"
        Scarpa Mojito Coral Red Der Scarpa Mojito von der italienischen Schuhfirma Scarpa hat sich zum Trend-Schuh entwickelt. Mit dem Focus auf fußgerechtes, ultrabequemes, individuelles Schuhwerk für längere Laufbelastung ist der Scarpa Mojito der perfekte Multifunktionsschuh für jedes Abenteuer. Geeignet für leichte Wanderungen und dem Zustieg zum Klettern. Aber der Scarpa Mojito ist auch für den Alltag bestens geeignet. description:
"
                                    The new Nike Free RUN draws upon new studies that reveal how the foot expands and contracts upon impact with the ground. For this reason, Nike designers have developed an auxetic midsole that allows it to splay upon impact without it thinning out (think about stretching an elastic band, which thins out when it’s pulled apart and is then compromised at its weakest point). Spreading across two planes, the geometric tri-star form mimics how the body and foot react to force and accounts for the massive changes in foot size (approximately one size in length and two sizes in width) that occur throughout a runner’s stride to deliver support and flexibility.Revolutionary, never before used Soft Foam provides comfort and cushioning without compromising natural motion.Offering breathability with an engineered mesh upper, the new Free RUN incorporates Flywire technology integrated with the laces for an adaptive, supportive fit.Features Include:Engineered mesh upper supports as it moves with you.Low-profile cushioning and rounded heel encourage natural footstrike.Auxetic tri-star outsole pattern expands with your step for flexible cushioning.Flywire technology integrated with the laces for an adaptive supportive fit.Offset: 8mm Last: QD-39
                                "@en

description:
"
                                    Ingannevoli di natura, le Nike Hypervenom Phantom II FG offrono un'agilità impareggiabile su terreni compatti e superfici naturali. La loro tomaia testurizzata NIKESKIN ottimizza la sensibilità e il controllo sulla palla. I cavi Flywire in combinazione con il collare Dynamic Fit avvolgono il piede per creare un ottimo supporto e stabilità. Essi sono incorporati su una forma anatomicamente studiate per la velocità che crea una calzata a pennello per la massima agilità. La tecnologia All Conditions Control (ACC) offre un controllo sulla palla costante in tutte le condizioni di tempo e i tacchetti hanno punte in TPU per una maggiore durabilità. Un'area con un'allacciatura ridotta crea una zona di battuta più ampia per massimizzare il contatto con la palla al fine di garantire che gli attacchi rimangono affidabili e raggiungono il loro obiettivo.All'interno della scarpa, una soletta preformata ammortizza il piede e aiuta a ridurre la pressione dei tacchetti, per un maggiore comfort e minori distrazioni.Un telaio in nylon con una base Pebax® offre un buon supporto pur mantenendo una sensibilità reattiva, mentre il design della piastra con alluce diviso serve per migliorare ulteriormente l'agilità.HYPERVENOM II – NON PUOI FERMARE QUELLO CHE NON PUOI VEDERE.

description:
"
                                    Parte di una serie di sette scarpe che rappresentano il progresso verso il successo di Cristiano Ronaldo, il Capitolo 3 si concentra sul gioco che lo ha portato all'attenzione di uno dei più grandi club al mondo.Per celebrare il momento della sua scoperta, le Nike Mercurial Superfly sono caratterizzate da una colorazione verde scuro che si ispira ai colori originali del club e sfumature neon che rappresentano il suo illustre talento. VESTIBILITÀSviluppate intorno all'idea di una prestazione da macchina da corsa, le Superfly V sono caratterizzate da una nuova forma V16, che è stata progettata per coinvolgere il metatarso, modellando la suola al naturale profilo del piede. Questo permette al metatarso di posizionarsi più in basso all'interno della scarpa, mentre l'alluce rimane leggermente sollevato in modo da  aumentare la flessibilità e generare la massima potenza negli scatti.Realizzate con una tomaia Flyknit e NikeSkin, le Superfly dispongono di una rinnovata costruzione priva di linguetta, mentre i cavi Flywire all'interno della tomaia sono indipendentemente in grado di reagire al modo in cui il piede interagisce con il terreno, per un bloccaggio ottimale.Per ridurre la perdita di elasticità nel tempo, il collo Dynamic Fit ha una struttura a maglia stretta per migliorare la propriocezione, mentre il suo tessuto interno antiscivolo elimina ogni movimento del piede all'interno della scarpa.TOCCOPer migliorare il tocco e la sensibilià, le Superfly V dispongono di un nuova costruzione testurizzata  3-D Speed Rub, che è lavorata a maglia nella tomaia in Flyknit per creare un maggiore attrito sulla palla in modo da ottimizzare il controllo ad alta velocità.Dotate di tecnologia (ACC) Tecnologia, le Superfly offrono una presa sulla palla affidabile in qualsiasi condizione di tempo.TRAZIONERiprogettato per migliorare l'accelerazione, il telaio delle Superfly è realizzato in Nylon compresso, che è 40% più leggero rispetto alla piastra in fibra di carbonio utilizzata per le Superfly IV.Più reattiva e di forma anatomical V-16, la piastra presenta tacchetti a forma di spina di pesce per una penetrazione, un rilascio e una frenata più rapidi su campi naturali compatti.
                                "@it

description:
"
                                    A newly designed tri-star outsole pattern adjusts to your foot's every step, delivering support and flexibility.The new Nike Free Run Flyknit draws upon new studies that reveal how the foot expands and contracts upon impact with the ground. For this reason, Nike designers have developed an auxetic midsole that allows it to splay upon impact without it thinning out (think about stretching an elastic band, which thins out when it’s pulled apart and is then compromised at its weakest point). Spreading across two planes, the geometric tri-star form mimics how the body and foot react to force and accounts for the massive changes in foot size (approximately one size in length and two sizes in width) that occur throughout a runner’s stride to deliver support and flexibility.Revolutionary, never before used Soft Foam provides comfort and cushioning without compromising natural motion.Flywire technology is integrated with the laces and Flyknit upper for a dynamic midfoot fit, along with asymmetrical lacing that follows the natural lines of the foot to help reduce lace pressure.Please be advised that the Nike Free shoe collection seems to be coming up slightly large by half a size and as a result we recommend considering half a size smaller.
                                "@en

"
                                    The saying “If it ain’t broke, don’t fix it” does not apply here for, while the HyperVenom was a superb boot in every way, Nike adopt the ethos that there is always room for improvement - Perfection Evolves.Introducing the HYPERVENOM II.Deceptive by nature, the Nike HyperVenom Phantom II Men's Soft-Ground Football Boot is built for unrivalled agility on soft, natural surfaces. Its new and improved honeycomb textured NikeSkin upper makes it easier to feel and control the ball, amplifying touch and control. The Flywire cables combined with the Dynamic Fit collar wrap the foot to create a supportive, locked-down feel. They are built on an anatomically correct contoured speed last creating a glove-like fit for maximum agility.The All Conditions Control (ACC) technology provides consistent ball control in both wet and dry conditions, while a mixture of fixed blades and detachable aluminium studs ensure reliable traction on soft natural ground.A shortened lace area creates a larger strike zone to give the purest contact with the ball to ensure that strikes stay true and find their target.Inside the boot, a moulded sock liner cushions the foot to help reduce pressure from studs, increasing comfort and reducing distractions, leaving you free to stay focused on the game.A Nylon chassis with a Pebax® base supports while retaining a responsive feel and the split-toe plate design serves to further improve agility.HYPERVENOM II - YOU CAN’T STOP WHAT YOU CAN’T SEE.

description:
"
FREE TO GO FURTHER
The Nike Free RN Distance Women's Running Shoe features Lunarlon cushioning with large hexagonal flex grooves for more natural motion with the soft comfort you need for longer runs.
Move Naturally
The natural-motion outsole features hexagonal flex grooves that offer six points of flexibility, allowing your feet to move the way they were meant to.
Soft Cushioning
The lightweight Lunarlon cushioning system delivers miles of soft responsiveness. It fuses soft foam and a lightweight Phylon carrier to deliver an excellent blend of plush comfort and durable support to go the distance.
Breathable Comfort
Single-layer, engineered knit helps keep your feet cool, while Flywire cables integrated with the laces wrap your arch for an adaptive, supportive fit.
More Details

Partial inner sleeve wraps your forefoot in breathable comfort
Deconstructed mesh heel provides support and breathability
Solid rubber segments under the toe for enhanced traction and durability
Anatomical heel enables more natural motion
Weight: 207 grams (women's size 5.5)

Nike Free Origins
After learning that Stanford athletes had been training barefoot on the university's golf course, three of Nike's most innovative and creative employees set out to develop a shoe that felt natural and weightless, similar to bare feet. The team spent eight years studying the biomechanics of runners' feet in motion. The results yielded a profound understanding of the foot's natural landing angle, pressure and toe position, allowing Nike designers to build an unconventional and flexible running shoe from the inside out. "@en

description:
"

Scarpe da running / corsa da donna Asics Gel Cumulus 17: la grande innovazione incontra le migliori caratteristiche di sempre!
La serie premiata di GEL-Cumulus continua a migliorare, con la diciassettesima versione che vanta un'intersuola FluidRide ™ top di gamma e unità di GEL Cushioning nel tallone e nell'avampiede ancora più grandi senza aumentare di peso. Inoltre, la Cumulus 17 risulta la versione più confortevole di sempre grazie alla costruzione senza cuciture. I corridori da neutri a lievemente pronatori resteranno attoniti indossando la versione più leggera e più ammortizzata della serie GEL-Cumulus mai creata.

Tecnologia applicata:
- La tecnologia FluidRide nell'intersuola fornisce l'ultima combinazione di rimbalzo e proprietà ammortizzanti con peso ridotto e una durata eccezionale. Lo strato superiore dell'intersuola è una gomma mescolata, fatta per massimizzare il comfort. Lo strato inferiore dell'intersuola è fatta da una gomma non miscelata più leggera e flessibile, permettendo la scarpa di offrire una maggiore reattività.
- Rearfoot and Forefoot GEL : L' ASICS GEL System è basato su un tipo speciale di silicone che funge da ottimo ammortizzatore per gli shock. Le unità di gel sono posizionate in modo strategico nell'intersuola per realizzare specifiche posizioni e funzioni.
- Guidance Trusstic System™: Il Trusstic System integra la costruzione Guidance Line per un'andatura migliorata in efficienza fornendo al contempo l'integrità strutturale al metatarso.
- Guidance Line ™: Scanalatura verticale di flessione per una maggiore efficienza nell'andatura.
- ASICS High Abrasion Resistance è una gomma posizionata nelle zone di maggior impatto della suola per ridurre l'eccessiva usura. AHAR+ è più sottile e leggera della AHAR
- Scanalature posizionate sotto l'avampiede ed il tallone per incrementare flessibilità ed ammortizzazione.
- I.G.S. (Impact Guidance System): Allo scopo di incontrare la domanda delle varie specialità dell'atletica l' I.G.S. (Impact Guidance System) è una filosofia di design ideata per seguire il movimento naturale del piede dell'atleta.
- ComforDry sockliner: offre un’ammortizzazione ottimale, creando un ambiente più fresco, asciutto e salutare per il piede.
- Occhielli dei lacci posizionati in modo indipendente per dare la giusta tensione, creando un ambiente su misura e maggiore comfort superiore.
- Seamless Construction: L'uso di materiali senza cuciture riduce il rischio di abrasioni e irritazioni.

Colore: Viola/Azzurro/Bianco.

description:
"
More cushioned than the Nike Free RN Motion Flyknit, the Nike Free RN Women's Running Shoe features a newly designed midsole pattern that expands, flexes and contracts with your foot with every step. Its lightweight, breathable mesh upper helps keep your feet cool and comfortable from start to finish.
MOVE NATURALLY
The next-generation Nike Free midsole expands in multiple directions thanks to an entirely new tri-star pattern, adding a new dimension of flexibility that lets your feet move more dynamically with every stride. Plus, the heel is rounded to mimic the shape of your foot and roll naturally with the ground.
SOFT CUSHIONING
Softer than previous iterations, the new midsole foam delivers exceptionally comfortable cushioning and lightweight durability for miles.
FLEXIBLE, BREATHABLE SUPPORT
Engineered mesh provides lightweight, flexible support and breathable comfort. Flywire cables integrate with the laces and can be adjusted for an adaptive fit.
MORE DETAILS

Minimal sockliner moulds to the shape of your foot for added support
Lightweight solid rubber segments under the toe and heel for enhanced traction and durability
Weight: 196 grams (women's size 5.5)

NIKE FREE ORIGINS
After learning that Stanford athletes had been training barefoot on the university's golf course, three of Nike's most innovative and creative employees set out to develop a shoe that felt natural and weightless, similar to bare feet. The team spent eight years studying the biomechanics of runners' feet in motion. The results yielded a profound understanding of the foot's natural landing angle, pressure and toe position, allowing Nike designers to build an unconventional and flexible running shoe from the inside out. "@en
title: "Nike Free RN Women's Running Shoes SU16 500"@en 500 · Nike Barefoot Trainers ah"@en

description:
"

Running shoes, Asics Gel-Noosa Tri model 11: comfort and cushioning for triathletes.
The new Gel-Noosa is specifically optimized for triathlon and Ironman races, with open mesh upper provides breathability and leaving feet dry and comfortable. In addition, the elastic strings and the upper grip, thanks to the absence of seams, ease the fit when dismounting from your bicycle. DuoMax midsole technology that provides an additional layer of support and stability.

Applied technology:
-Enhanced upper for a better fit with the tab that does not flow inward.
-Enhanced upper, open mesh knitted without seams, to reduce friction and to give greater comfort.
-I.G.S. (Impact Guidance System): in order to meet the demand of various specialities of Athletics the I.G.S. (Impact Guidance System) & andserious; a design philosophy designed to follow the natural movement of the athlete's foot.
-3M reflectivity: AHAR rubber material placed in the heel with high abrasion resistance for added durability and a cushioned.
-Cable Propulsion Plate which improves the separation in racing at a fast pace
-ASICS High Abrasion Resistance rubber is placed in areas of greatest impact of the outsole to reduce excessive wear. AHAR + is thinner and lighter than the AHAR.
-Automatic Guidance Line: since the previous release the Guidance Line was stretched to encompass the heel area. A special space that follows the natural change in pressure from heel to toe that occurs during the ride. The result is a midsole with greater adaptability towards the running style of each runner. Automatic Guidance Line and is; a great help in maintaining a natural ride even over long distances
-Exclusive Asics cushioning material Solyte: offering a lightweight midsole and a property of "compression" excellent, combined with extraordinary durability.
-GEL cushioning system: attenuates shock during impact and help the movement in multiple planes as it does during the gait cycle.
-Dynamic DuoMax: it is an exclusive system which consists of two different density midsole material and is designed to control a slight hyper-pronation.

Color: Black/White/Grey/Blue

"@en
title: "ASICS GEL NOOSA TRI 11"@en 11 - MAN RUNNING SHOES Asics colour Multicolor T626N 9601 Athletic footwear apparel and sports equipment"@en

description:
"

La linguetta delle scarpe mimica la bandiera nazionale della terra del Sol Levante, mentre un tradizionale simbolo 'inkan' e un tallone a scaglie eccentuano il carattere mitico del Giappone. Progettate da Puma per i giocatori più veloci in campo, le evoSPEED 1.3 X-Ray sono tra le più leggere scarpe da calcio per terreni compatti e sono caratterizzate da una tomaia in microfibra liscia che crea una sensazione come a piedi nudi. La suola anatomica progettata sul modello 1.3 dispone di una spina dorsale Pebax Speedtrack per una migliore rotazione e reattività. description:
"
                                    Puma Suede Classic+ - Cabernet/White Worn by athletic greats such as basketball's Walt 'Clyde' Frazier and the track 's Tommie Smith, it rose to new levels of fame in the early days of b-boys and funk beats. As this underground music scene rose to the street surface, the Puma Suede started making moves among break dance crews and hip-hop club-goers.This revolution, like others, disrupted the norm. It followed the logic of the decade. And so did PUMA. Puma felt the culture shift beneath their feet from strict convention into self-expression. They responded by translating sports gear into street wear.The Puma Suede tells the story of sport-inspired style. This time-honoured member of the PUMA Archive continues to evolve with the times while maintaining its smooth silhouette, swagger and grit. The Puma Suede proves that no matter the decade, the city, the continent -style can be revolutionary.Early break dance crews whole-heartedly adopted the Puma Suede for its sweet tread and smooth, classic look. Basketball legend Walt 'Clyde' Frazier inspired PUMA's infamous 'Clyde' silhouette and made some of his best moves in the Puma Suede.'B-Boy' is short for 'break-boy ' as in 'a break dancing boy'. A growing number of 'B-Girls' are currently on the rise. In a past life, the Puma Suede was a sport hero: In 1968, it was worn by track and field champion Tommie Smith at the Summer Games.'Airtracks' are said to be the toughest and most dangerous break dance moves in existence - cue the Puma Suede treads for traction and take-off.Features Include:100% Suede upper for optimum comfortCentrally-positioned lacing with broad laces for a perfect fitNon-slip and abrasion-resistant outer sole made from 100% RubberPUMA formstrip PUMA Suede archive logo and PUMA Cat logo
                                "@en
